7. Recommendation letters (at least 2) (The recommendation letters should be submitted
electronically by the referral before the application deadline. You may find the submission link
for recommendation letters at the online application submission webpage – see section 7
below) (compulsory)
8. Scanned copy of ID (for Greek citizens), passport (for EU and non-EU citizens) (compulsory)
9. Undergraduate/bachelor degree thesis (optional)
10. Related to biomedical engineering research activity (optional)
11. Related to biomedical engineering professional activity (optional)
12. Related to biomedical engineering internship(s) (optional)
13. Other related to biomedical engineering activity (optional)
